1
00:00:14,725 --> 00:00:18,487
♪Allergic to fast-food love,
even if it's too naive♪

2
00:00:18,562 --> 00:00:22,162
♪Just like a hug needs
the right body heat♪

3
00:00:22,287 --> 00:00:25,437
♪Your “same here” carries
a touch of resolve♪

4
00:00:25,862 --> 00:00:29,412
♪Pack my bags,
we can set off right now♪

5
00:00:29,637 --> 00:00:33,112
♪The future is a wondrous,
unknown adventure♪

6
00:00:33,250 --> 00:00:36,712
♪The journey itself is what truly matters
before the destination♪

7
00:00:36,787 --> 00:00:40,975
♪Those moments together
are what bind us strongest♪

8
00:00:41,025 --> 00:00:42,612
♪Connect♪

9
00:00:42,625 --> 00:00:43,275
♪Let's go!♪

10
00:00:43,612 --> 00:00:47,137
♪Leave worries behind
in yesterday's sentimentality♪

11
00:00:47,237 --> 00:00:50,675
♪Today, no dwelling on
negative emotions♪

12
00:00:50,750 --> 00:00:53,450
♪Tomorrow holds more luck♪

13
00:00:53,450 --> 00:00:55,262
♪Together we'll create moving melodies♪

14
00:00:55,262 --> 00:00:58,199
♪The future begins to take shape♪

15
00:00:59,075 --> 00:01:02,375
=Love in A Secret=
(I Just Want to Drown With You)

16
00:01:02,675 --> 00:01:06,262
=Episode 21=

17
00:01:23,480 --> 00:01:24,000
Ms. Lu,

18
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:26,080
do you need me to call your family
to pick you up?

19
00:01:32,175 --> 00:01:33,800
I'm a grown-up.

20
00:01:34,637 --> 00:01:35,694
Why call my parents?

21
00:01:38,150 --> 00:01:39,510
Pick me up from school?

22
00:01:39,960 --> 00:01:41,080
That's not what I meant.

23
00:01:41,080 --> 00:01:42,120
I'm sorry, Ms. Lu.

24
00:01:46,800 --> 00:01:48,350
Have you had your heart broken?

25
00:01:50,750 --> 00:01:52,600
Do you know how it feels?

26
00:02:02,160 --> 00:02:03,920
Like a knife

27
00:02:04,625 --> 00:02:07,465
stabbing into your chest
again and again.

28
00:02:10,440 --> 00:02:12,400
Slicing you inch by inch.

29
00:02:16,237 --> 00:02:19,117
All you can do is watch
as flesh and blood scatter.

30
00:02:20,512 --> 00:02:21,525
No anesthesia.

31
00:02:24,440 --> 00:02:25,720
No chance to breathe.

32
00:02:29,700 --> 00:02:30,500
Forget it.

33
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:32,990
You wouldn't understand.

34
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:46,520
Are you okay, Ms. Lu?

35
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:52,912
(I used the most despicable method)

36
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:55,360
(to make you withdraw
from our relationship.)

37
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:57,520
(I know you're in pain.)

38
00:02:58,640 --> 00:02:59,320
(So am I.)

39
00:03:03,720 --> 00:03:05,440
(Sun, don't resent me.)

40
00:03:05,875 --> 00:03:08,487
(And don't meet me again.)

41
00:03:08,612 --> 00:03:09,612
Man.

42
00:03:31,480 --> 00:03:33,640
Why have you looked thinner
over the past few days?

43
00:03:33,960 --> 00:03:35,720
When you get there, eat properly.

44
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:42,800
What are you doing here?

45
00:03:43,840 --> 00:03:45,160
What are you saying, Lu?

46
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:46,680
She's your brother's fiancée.

47
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:48,440
What's so surprising
about her coming over?

48
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:53,160
You're up.

49
00:03:58,160 --> 00:03:58,960
Lu,

50
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:00,960
Man and Lily

51
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:02,960
are going to the US to register
their marriage.

52
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:03,920
They're leaving soon.

53
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:05,920
Well...

54
00:04:41,200 --> 00:04:42,480
This girl.

55
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:44,360
I don't know
what's wrong with her today.

56
00:04:47,840 --> 00:04:48,960
Ze,

57
00:04:49,640 --> 00:04:50,720
help me.

58
00:04:56,760 --> 00:04:59,280
Zhu, you must be hospitalized.

59
00:05:00,000 --> 00:05:02,840
Ze, sorry to trouble you again.

60
00:05:03,640 --> 00:05:05,480
If you keep going like this,

61
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:07,320
I won't hide it from Mr. Lu anymore.

62
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:09,160
I'll tell him the truth
about your condition.

63
00:05:09,800 --> 00:05:10,920
No.

64
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:13,840
You're fainting more
and more frequently.

65
00:05:13,840 --> 00:05:14,720
The doctor says

66
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:16,400
if you don't undergo
inpatient treatment,

67
00:05:16,700 --> 00:05:17,380
you...

68
00:05:19,787 --> 00:05:20,787
I will die?

69
00:05:25,440 --> 00:05:27,087
Death isn't scary.

70
00:05:28,880 --> 00:05:30,160
Living is.

71
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:34,240
Zhu,

72
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:36,320
you're nothing like the Lu Zhu

73
00:05:36,320 --> 00:05:37,560
in my memory.

74
00:05:38,760 --> 00:05:39,800
What was she like?

75
00:05:41,280 --> 00:05:42,920
The Lu Zhu I remember

76
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:45,160
wasn't this negative.

77
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:46,960
She wouldn't treat herself so harshly.

78
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:49,480
Why are you doing this?

79
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:50,760
For your brother,

80
00:05:50,760 --> 00:05:51,720
Ye Man?

81
00:05:57,640 --> 00:05:59,000
Has it occurred to you

82
00:06:00,960 --> 00:06:02,680
that maybe I'm not who you think I am?

83
00:06:07,760 --> 00:06:08,560
Ze,

84
00:06:09,320 --> 00:06:10,520
I'm joking.

85
00:06:11,760 --> 00:06:12,880
I promise you.

86
00:06:13,320 --> 00:06:16,480
I'll adjust and get treatment.

87
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:19,130
I just had my heart broken, that's all.

88
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:23,520
Alright. Don't look so miserable.

89
00:06:23,520 --> 00:06:24,680
Smile.

90
00:06:29,280 --> 00:06:30,080
Alright.

91
00:06:30,450 --> 00:06:32,370
I'll go find the doctor.

92
00:06:32,880 --> 00:06:33,840
Take a rest.

93
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:52,800
Hello, Ye Man?

94
00:06:53,680 --> 00:06:54,520
Where are you?

95
00:06:55,840 --> 00:06:57,560
I'm out with Lily.

96
00:06:58,880 --> 00:06:59,840
I need to see you.

97
00:07:01,187 --> 00:07:02,027
What is it?

98
00:07:03,640 --> 00:07:04,440
Lu Zhu is sick.

99
00:07:04,440 --> 00:07:05,680
Do you know?

100
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,520
(You once said)

101
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:11,080
(the rain falling from the sky
has no roots.)

102
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:15,360
(Those wandering souls
unwilling to leave)

103
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:17,920
(will follow the rain-soaked road)

104
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:19,520
(to find their loved ones.)

105
00:07:20,680 --> 00:07:22,320
(If I die,)

106
00:07:23,480 --> 00:07:25,320
(when it rains,)

107
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:29,040
(will I be able to find you?)

108
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:48,480
Mr. Lu,

109
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:51,520
I don't want to hide
my feelings anymore.

110
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:54,080
Lu has run toward me again and again.

111
00:07:56,440 --> 00:07:57,240
This time,

112
00:07:58,500 --> 00:08:00,290
I want to run toward her,
no matter the cost.

113
00:08:01,200 --> 00:08:02,360
No matter the cost?

114
00:08:06,750 --> 00:08:08,725
Do you know what that means?

115
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:13,360
Do you know the position
the Lu Group holds in Hai City?

116
00:08:13,760 --> 00:08:16,160
Do you know the impact this relationship

117
00:08:16,760 --> 00:08:19,360
will have on the company?

118
00:08:21,080 --> 00:08:21,880
I know.

119
00:08:23,640 --> 00:08:24,760
Of course I know

120
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:27,680
how this will

121
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:29,920
affect you

122
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:31,320
and the Lu Group.

123
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:32,560
That's why

124
00:08:32,560 --> 00:08:35,160
Lu and I have been on and off.

125
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:37,320
But have you ever considered our future?

126
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:39,160
That's not for me to consider.

127
00:08:41,160 --> 00:08:43,360
You young people are too selfish.

128
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:45,840
You only think about your own feelings.

129
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:51,480
I built the Lu Group with my own hands.

130
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:54,640
I won't let it collapse overnight

131
00:08:54,640 --> 00:08:55,720
because of

132
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:57,360
your scandal.

133
00:08:58,625 --> 00:08:59,585
Man,

134
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:02,160
you're a good child.

135
00:09:02,160 --> 00:09:03,720
I've always thought highly of you.

136
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:06,120
For your future

137
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:06,920
and your career,

138
00:09:07,680 --> 00:09:09,800
this relationship isn't worth it.

139
00:09:13,520 --> 00:09:14,320
Mr. Lu,

140
00:09:16,280 --> 00:09:17,240
maybe in your heart,

141
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:20,000
love isn't important.

142
00:09:21,040 --> 00:09:22,800
But to Lu and me,

143
00:09:23,880 --> 00:09:26,640
and to those selfish people
you mentioned,

144
00:09:27,240 --> 00:09:28,720
love is more important than anything.

145
00:09:30,280 --> 00:09:31,360
I will love her forever.

146
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:35,640
When the sun rises,

147
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:38,520
I'll take her to chase the sunrise.

148
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:42,240
When the sun sets,

149
00:09:44,680 --> 00:09:46,120
I'll take her to chase the sunset.

150
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:49,680
When it rains,

151
00:09:51,040 --> 00:09:52,480
I'll walk with her in the rain.

152
00:09:55,280 --> 00:09:56,600
When the wind blows,

153
00:10:00,800 --> 00:10:02,000
I won't let her catch a cold.

154
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:07,760
I'm willing

155
00:10:07,760 --> 00:10:09,360
to pour my most sincere feelings

156
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:13,000
into her entire life.

157
00:10:14,120 --> 00:10:15,520
That's my promise to you

158
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:17,360
and to Lu.

159
00:10:21,280 --> 00:10:23,520
How beautiful.

160
00:10:23,520 --> 00:10:25,920
You almost moved me.

161
00:10:25,920 --> 00:10:27,720
But you've forgotten one thing.

162
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:29,880
What your father did,

163
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:32,040
his debts,

164
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:33,840
and his death,

165
00:10:34,880 --> 00:10:35,720
have you

166
00:10:37,640 --> 00:10:38,680
forgotten them?

167
00:10:39,920 --> 00:10:40,880
Man,

168
00:10:41,040 --> 00:10:42,840
with that amount of debt,

169
00:10:42,840 --> 00:10:44,680
you couldn't repay it
in several lifetimes.

170
00:10:45,160 --> 00:10:47,760
If you have no power or status,

171
00:10:48,040 --> 00:10:51,640
what will you use to guarantee
Lu's happiness?

172
00:10:51,640 --> 00:10:53,080
Huh?

173
00:10:57,360 --> 00:10:58,320
So in your eyes,

174
00:10:59,280 --> 00:11:00,312
people without power

175
00:11:00,312 --> 00:11:01,920
don't deserve to be happy?

176
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:04,320
My dad built a successful career.

177
00:11:04,320 --> 00:11:05,960
But what did he get in the end?

178
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:10,840
I was guilt-tripped before.

179
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:13,520
I thought leaving Lu

180
00:11:13,520 --> 00:11:14,600
would make her happy.

181
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:16,040
But it doesn't work like this.

182
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:21,820
When you fall in love with someone,
how can you forget them so easily?

183
00:11:23,760 --> 00:11:25,400
I can't keep pretending anymore.

184
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:27,120
And Mr. Lu,

185
00:11:27,920 --> 00:11:29,360
let me ask you something.

186
00:11:30,120 --> 00:11:32,400
When your career was thriving,

187
00:11:33,020 --> 00:11:34,840
and the people you loved
left you one by one,

188
00:11:34,840 --> 00:11:36,200
what could you do?

189
00:11:37,040 --> 00:11:37,520
Dad!

190
00:11:37,520 --> 00:11:38,560
Get up!

191
00:11:39,200 --> 00:11:40,400
- Dad!
- Get up!

192
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:49,920
You keep making all these claims,

193
00:11:50,280 --> 00:11:51,400
what are you trying to prove?

194
00:11:51,800 --> 00:11:53,920
That you treat Lu well?

195
00:11:54,280 --> 00:11:55,920
That everything you say is right?

196
00:11:56,000 --> 00:11:58,280
That we're all wrong?

197
00:11:58,840 --> 00:12:01,600
If you think our love is wrong,

198
00:12:04,040 --> 00:12:06,120
there's something else you should know.

199
00:12:08,560 --> 00:12:10,000
Nineteen years ago,

200
00:12:11,680 --> 00:12:13,760
Mom was pregnant with twins.

201
00:12:15,680 --> 00:12:16,960
One was named Lu Zhu,

202
00:12:18,840 --> 00:12:20,040
and the other Lu Sun.

203
00:12:20,440 --> 00:12:22,320
But after she became pregnant,

204
00:12:23,040 --> 00:12:25,440
she suffered from
severe postpartum depression.

205
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:28,080
When she needed you the most,

206
00:12:28,680 --> 00:12:29,600
you weren't there.

207
00:12:30,360 --> 00:12:31,920
But she couldn't leave you,

208
00:12:32,160 --> 00:12:36,280
so she made a very, very bad decision.

209
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:39,640
That's to send me away.

210
00:12:49,762 --> 00:12:54,262
♪Bit by bit, I'll forget you♪

211
00:12:54,487 --> 00:12:58,275
♪Bit by bit, I'll erase the memories♪

212
00:12:58,450 --> 00:13:02,525
♪From now on,
your image won't linger in my mind♪

213
00:13:02,525 --> 00:13:06,662
♪Nor will those fragments of the past♪

214
00:13:06,787 --> 00:13:10,562
♪Days will slowly drift away
like passing clouds♪

215
00:13:10,562 --> 00:13:14,337
♪I'll learn to stop longing for
what's gone♪

216
00:13:14,337 --> 00:13:16,612
♪The you in my memories♪

217
00:13:16,612 --> 00:13:18,625
♪Will fade from clarity♪

218
00:13:18,625 --> 00:13:24,062
♪How much longer must I wait to♪

219
00:13:25,625 --> 00:13:31,062
♪Forget you completely?♪
